Name: Type.Property.ValueTypes
Description: Illustrates various property types for models

Enums.Name: FixedInnerEnum
Enums.Description: Enum that will be used as a property for model EnumProperty. Non-extensible.

Enums.Name: InnerEnum
Enums.Description: Enum that will be used as a property for model EnumProperty. Non-extensible.

Type.Name: InnerModel
Type.Description: Inner model. Will be a property type for ModelWithModelProperties

Models.Name: NeverProperty
Models.Description: Model with a property never. (This property should not be included).

Models.Name: UnknownStringProperty
Models.Description: Model with a property unknown, and the data is a string.

Models.Name: UnknownIntProperty
Models.Description: Model with a property unknown, and the data is a int32.

Models.Name: UnknownDictProperty
Models.Description: Model with a property unknown, and the data is a dictionnary.

Models.Name: UnknownArrayProperty
Models.Description: Model with a property unknown, and the data is an array.
